form.prompt_placeholder: Black and white line art style, pure line expression with no color blocks or grayscale gradients. Lines are crisp and sharp with clean, unblurred edges; clear contrast in line weight (bold, heavy contour lines for main subjects, delicate thin lines for decorative details); moderate line density with precise rendering of key structures (such as muscle anatomy, fabric folds, and scene perspective), free of redundant stray lines; the artwork balances realism with clean precision, featuring complete contours and clearly distinguishable detail textures (such as fabric weaves and metallic lines); overall style is concise and powerful with distinct visual hierarchy, background lines can be appropriately simplified to emphasize the main subject.
